      <title>哈马斯称以色列袭击加沙学校造成 100 名巴勒斯坦人死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-10/israel-strike-on-gaza-school-kills-100-palestinians-hamas-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哈马斯称，以色列周六早晨袭击了加沙市的一所学校，造成约 100 名巴勒斯坦人在祈祷时死亡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-10/israel-strike-on-gaza-school-kills-100-palestinians-hamas-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 10 Aug 2024 04:45:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>朝鲜领导人将洪水灾民转移至首都，拒绝外界援助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-08-10/north-korean-leader-says-thousands-of-flood-victims-will-be-brought-to-capital-for-temporary-care</link>
      <description><![CDATA[首尔，韩国（美联社） — 朝鲜领导人金正恩表示，朝鲜不会寻求外部帮助来恢复该国与中国边境附近地区遭受的洪水灾害，并命令官员将数千名流离失所的居民转移到首都，为他们提供更好的照顾。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-08-10/north-korean-leader-says-thousands-of-flood-victims-will-be-brought-to-capital-for-temporary-care</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 10 Aug 2024 04:01:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国暴乱案定罪后，YouTube 上仍保留仇恨视频</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-10/youtube-hate-video-remained-up-even-after-uk-riot-conviction</link>
      <description><![CDATA[8 月 5 日晚，亚伦·约翰逊抵达英格兰北部斯托克波特的不列颠尼亚酒店。这位来自附近地区的 32 岁男子来这里是为了看看他所说的“移民酒店”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-10/youtube-hate-video-remained-up-even-after-uk-riot-conviction</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 10 Aug 2024 04:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾计划在越南举行联合演习后开展更多海上活动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-10/philippines-plans-more-sea-activities-with-vietnam-after-drills</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾海岸警卫队表示，菲律宾和越南本周在存在海上争端的情况下举行了联合演习，海岸警卫队计划今年晚些时候派遣一艘船前往越南，以加强海上合作。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-10/philippines-plans-more-sea-activities-with-vietnam-after-drills</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 10 Aug 2024 01:35:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>前往中东的美国航母上的水兵做好冲突准备</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-09/sailors-on-us-carrier-headed-for-middle-east-brace-for-conflict</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当亚伯拉罕·林肯号航空母舰撤出关岛时，该航空母舰的船长通过对讲机向船员宣布，美国对中东地区胡塞导弹和无人机发动的新一轮打击“提醒了我们将要面临的环境”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-09/sailors-on-us-carrier-headed-for-middle-east-brace-for-conflict</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯称增援部队已抵达以抵抗乌克兰入侵</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-09/russia-s-lipetsk-evacuates-people-after-drone-attack-on-airfield</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯派遣军事增援部队，与乌克兰军队在俄罗斯西部库尔斯克地区进行对峙，这是自第二次世界大战以来外国首次入侵其领土。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-09/russia-s-lipetsk-evacuates-people-after-drone-attack-on-airfield</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 04:41:51 GMT</pubDate>
